            . On 12th of July, about eleven o'clock in the morning, I was in <placeName id="t18180909-28-crimeloc162">Charles-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18180909-28-crimeloc162" type="placeName" value="Charles-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18180909-28-crimeloc162" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-28-off160 t18180909-28-crimeloc162"></join>, looking at the fire, a boy came up, and told me my pocket had been picked - I missed my handkerchief - He pointed the prisoner out to me, who was running; I pursued and took him; my handkerchief was found in his bosom.</p>
               <p>EDWARD STEPHENSON. I saw the prisoner take the handkerchief out of the prosecutor's pocket, and told him; he immediately took the prisoner, and found the handkerchief in his bosom.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
